title: Awful
review: This was a terrible waste of my sunday evening. I couldn't even finish this movie. The acting is terrible. The movie is boring and uneventful. I would never recommend this movie.

title: Fun Watch!
review:
This is a really solid and an entertaining watch, especially if you love combat/action like myself.

I throughly loved how the meat of action and plot happened in one location. It allows for the story to be simple, honest and unique.

Bonus points for Kevin Nash (I grew up watching and being a fan of WCW/WWE so it was pretty dope to see him in it #WolfPack).
